
Add a column in a existing table:-
ALTER TABLE USER_REGISTRATION 
  ADD PHONENO INTEGER(12);

1.Drop a Column:-
ALTER TABLE "table_name" DROP "column_name";


UPDATE USER_REGISTRATION SET PHONENO =12344 and USERNAME ='bejnath' WHERE EmailId ='b1@b1.com';



Truncate/ To delete records from tables:-

1. DELETE FROM table_name
WHERE condition;


Delete a Table:-
drop table InvitationTable;



